high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the kitchen island, then walk around to the other side of the kitchen island.
Pick up the metal table spoon off of the kitchen island.
Turn right and walk to the kitchen sink.
Put the spoon in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean spoon.
Turn around and walk back over to the side of the kitchen island.
Put the clean metal spoon standing up on the kitchen island.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean metal spoon on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Turn right walk forward then, turn around the table
Pick up the spoon on the table
Turn right then go to the sink
Put the spoon in the sink and rinse it
Turn left then head to the table
Put the spoon on the table beside the knife on the left side
anns.task_desc: Put the clean spoon on the table

high_descs: Turn around and go to the other side of the kitchen island.
Pick up the spoon from the kitchen island.
Turn right and go to the sink.
Put the spoon in the sink, rinse it off and pick it back up.
Turn around and go back to the kitchen island.
Put the spoon on the kitchen island.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed spoon on the kitchen island.
